    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Be a slime!</strong></u> <br>Bounce around the city and squeeze your way wherever you want to go! (• ᴗ •)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321330/extras/be_slime_new_rounded.gif?t=1759967283\" /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strand type online experience: You can collect coins when other players spend theirs, and work together to unlock new buildings ( Work in progress ) <strong>(⌐■_■)</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Collect Gachapon!</strong></u> <br>Collect Japanese capsule toys with satisfying Gacha-Pon sounds <strong>(♡‿♡)</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321330/extras/gacha_rounded.gif?t=1759967283\" /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find 23 unique collectible items + more in progress <strong>w(°ｏ°)w</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Manage a Japanese Vending Machine corner store </strong></u> <br>Take over a creepy corner store full of vending machines and sell drinks to fellow slimes! <strong>＼($ヮ$)/</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321330/extras/fm_rounded.gif?t=1759967283\" /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring music by Keisuke Ito and DOS-88 <strong>~(˘▽˘~)♪♪♪</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Unlock the mega chicken sushi chef! </u></strong>  <br>Watch the sushi go around  as your slime customers grow with happiness <strong>(っ ᵔ◡ᵔ)っ</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321330/extras/kaiten_rounded.gif?t=1759967283\" /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We haven't developed the technology to actually taste the food or drinks yet. <strong>(×_×)</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><i>Squeeze the day - add to your wishlist now!</i></strong></h2></li></ul>",
